Package game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DrawingSurface
    Draws all the things that will be displayed on the window UI, players, and map are drawn Draws a server window too
    Entity
    Defines an entity that is drawn onto the world map and can interact with other entities
    Game
    Creates a server, client and drawing surface Also creates a menu for player inputs
    Main
    This class runs the game class
    Menu
    Creates a menu that takes in a username, ip address, and sets whether you are a zombie or not
    MovingEntity
    A specific type of Entity that can translate about the map and interact with other Entities
    Player
    Represents a player, a player can be either a surivor or zombie
    StaticEntity
    A specific type of Entity that can not move or translate about the world
    Survivor
    A MovingEntity that can interact with other Entities Survivors can attack zombies with a gun and have a certain number of bullets associated with them
    Wall
    A wall that can be created like the one on the border with the US and Mexico :D
    Zombie
    A MovingEntity that can interact with other Entities Zombies can attack survivors and damage them if they touch them
